  "3277670": {
    "name": "可爱追逃记",
    "steam_appid": 3277670,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >欢迎进入《<i>可爱追逃记</i>》的奇妙世界！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这个迷人的俯视角冒险中，玩家可以选择扮演狡猾的蛇或灵活的苹果，在时间和陷阱的挑战中展开较量。带给玩家充满挑战与乐趣的竞技体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>玩家将控制一只灵活的小蛇追逐一只机智的苹果，避免被苹果反击，同时在充满陷阱和敌人的关卡中不断挑战自我。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277670/extras/206bd530d880345a0e4631e0a6dafa40.poster.avif?t=1741316743\" width=254 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277670/extras/206bd530d880345a0e4631e0a6dafa40.webm?t=1741316743\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277670/extras/206bd530d880345a0e4631e0a6dafa40.mp4?t=1741316743\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>游戏提供双人合作与竞争模式，也支持单人模式与AI对战。无论是与朋友同屏竞技，还是独自挑战，都能享受无与伦比的游戏乐趣！</i></strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏模式：</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>单人模式：</strong> 与AI对抗，挑战自我，分别扮演蛇和苹果。你能否智胜AI，成为终极逃生者？</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>本地多人模式：</strong> 和朋友一起合作竞争！在紧张刺激的追逐战中体验乐趣。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277670/extras/6d2b56c71a9c66524e5faf122d76de5c.poster.avif?t=1741316743\" width=800 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277670/extras/6d2b56c71a9c66524e5faf122d76de5c.webm?t=1741316743\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277670/extras/6d2b56c71a9c66524e5faf122d76de5c.mp4?t=1741316743\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏特色：</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>蛇 vs 苹果模式：</strong> 追逐与反击的紧张对战，苹果也能反击哦！避开火球，争取胜利！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>双蛇模式：</strong> 经典的现代版贪吃蛇玩法，撞到对方尾巴即为失败，挑战朋友的操作极限！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>生存模式：</strong> 蛇与苹果并肩合作，一起抵挡不断增加的敌人和陷阱，考验团队默契与生存策略！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>丰富的敌人和陷阱：</strong> 各式敌人和天降流星、火炮射击等陷阱让每一局都充满惊险与乐趣。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>道具与加成：</strong> 收集金币和宝箱，获得速度提升、喷火球等强力道具，改变游戏的战局。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Steam成就系统：</strong> 挑战自我，解锁各种成就，证明你是最强的玩家！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277670/extras/2f07702bd21c56f5a9f7e95929de3b7f.poster.avif?t=1741316743\" width=552 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277670/extras/2f07702bd21c56f5a9f7e95929de3b7f.webm?t=1741316743\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277670/extras/2f07702bd21c56f5a9f7e95929de3b7f.mp4?t=1741316743\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>玩法特色：</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>动态追逐机制：</strong> 蛇必须追捕苹果，同时避开各种陷阱，如流星和落石。小心那些发射岩石和火球的炮台，以及可能致命的死胡同！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>收集品和强化道具：</strong> 收集散布在地图上的硬币，提升速度，并在衣柜系统中解锁各种时尚帽子。探索宝箱，获取额外生命、速度提升和临时火球能力。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>耐力与冲刺：</strong> 明智地使用你的耐力！快速奔跑，争取胜利，但要留意耐力值——合理管理能量以超越对手。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>紧张的游戏结束阶段：</strong> 当倒计时进入最后30秒，游戏将加速！蛇和苹果的速度提升，音乐的音调也随之上升，带来更高的紧张感。</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>多样地图：</strong> </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >春天的草地、夏日的酷热、秋日的温暖阳光等多张地图，各具特色，带来不同的游戏体验。</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>换装系统：</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家可以使用金币购买并自由更换角色的帽子。每个帽子都有独特的可爱装扮，玩家可以在游戏中自由搭配，打造专属的个性造型，享受换装带来的乐趣与创意。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277670/extras/3b2bb5fbd14f271e3d0f666e94c26138.poster.avif?t=1741316743\" width=678 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277670/extras/3b2bb5fbd14f271e3d0f666e94c26138.webm?t=1741316743\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277670/extras/3b2bb5fbd14f271e3d0f666e94c26138.mp4?t=1741316743\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>武器系统：</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家可以使用金币购买并自由更换角色的武器。每个武器都有独特的技能，例如火球，炸弹，电浆等，玩家可以在游戏中自由搭配，打造专属的配装，享受换装带来的乐趣与创意。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277670/extras/0b289502e11ca230ab78681b705f0ce2.avif?t=1741316743\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277670/extras_big/0b289502e11ca230ab78681b705f0ce2.avif?t=1741316743 width=800 height=440 /></span></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>控制方式：</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >支持手柄操作</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >支持同一键盘双人对战</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>难度调整：</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多种难度选择，可以根据个人喜好调节，延长游戏时间或挑战极限。</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>敌人类型：</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >史莱姆、松鼠、乌龟等形象可爱但极具挑战的敌人，不同的攻击方式让每一场战斗充满变数。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >加入《<i>可爱追逃记</i>》的乐趣——每场比赛都是心跳加速的追逐！你能成为捕捉苹果的蛇，还是能智胜蛇并赢得胜利的苹果？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>准备好迎接终极对决吧！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>特别感谢我的朋友 <strong>Robin Lyu</strong>，为我精心制作了精彩的宣传片！你的创意和努力让游戏焕发出独特的魅力，我由衷感激你的付出！</i></p>",
